I would say that I can improve on this by playing 16. ...Nxc5. Keeping the c file open and creating a nice advanced post for my knight.  The advantage of Nxc5 is that my knight would be able to jump to D5 were it would dominate the board. I also have prepared a positional trap in case of 17. Rxd6.
